that we've done this before.

00:03:20.050 --> 00:03:21.980
We freaked out
about media before.

00:03:21.980 --> 00:03:22.660
And guess what?

00:03:22.660 --> 00:03:24.266
The romantic novel,
one of the books

00:03:24.266 --> 00:03:26.140
they were freaking out
about was Jane Austen,

00:03:26.140 --> 00:03:27.350
one of the authors.

00:03:27.350 --> 00:03:30.590
I would die for my daughter
to read Jane Austen now.

00:03:30.590 --> 00:03:33.720
I have a 16-year-old, by
the way, and a 13-year-old.

00:03:33.720 --> 00:03:38.200
So it happens over, and
over, and over again.

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:41.260
The more things change, the
more they stay the same.

