about it, a book

00:07:53.310 --> 00:07:55.620
is a much better way
to ignore people.

00:07:55.620 --> 00:07:58.660
So the good old days when we
ignored each other with books

00:07:58.660 --> 00:08:00.990
instead of smartphones.

00:08:00.990 --> 00:08:07.250
