what you guys probably do,

00:08:07.250 --> 00:08:11.000
and it shows that all of these
different applications, they're

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:13.910
just extensions of things
that are old school.

00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:16.220
So YouTube, we used to
just be able to look

00:08:16.220 --> 00:08:17.240
in front of ourselves.

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:19.350
Now we can access the world.

00:08:19.350 --> 00:08:24.390
Facebook, our kids
now are in contact,

00:08:24.390 --> 00:08:29.050
if they're on Facebook, with
everyone they've known forever.

00:08:29.050 --> 00:08:31.680
