kids, the parents,

00:10:07.780 --> 00:10:10.780
this one I'm assuming
you have younger kids.

00:10:10.780 --> 00:10:12.350
I talk about all sorts of stuff.

00:10:12.350 --> 00:10:14.030
There are all sorts of tips.

00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:16.740
