basic ones that I think fit

00:10:16.740 --> 00:10:18.090
with almost everybody.

00:10:18.090 --> 00:10:19.850
So be a responsible role model.

00:10:19.850 --> 00:10:22.110
That's number one, and
I'm gonna hit that hard.

00:10:22.110 --> 00:10:23.870
