get distracted by their phones.

00:11:16.620 --> 00:11:19.550
I know it's really easy
to look at your phone

00:11:19.550 --> 00:11:22.040
and be distracted, and
not be there for your kid,

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:23.140
but they notice.

00:11:23.140 --> 00:11:26.560
They notice, and they start
noticing at a very young age.

