00:21:32.370 --> 00:21:34.020
in a classroom studying math.

00:21:34.020 --> 00:21:38.940
So it was very, very high effect
for a short amount of time.

00:21:38.940 --> 00:21:41.280
So brief, high quality
parent-child interactions

00:21:41.280 --> 00:21:44.540
about math can break the
intergenerational cycle

00:21:44.540 --> 00:21:46.832
of low math achievement.

00:21:46.832 --> 00:21:49.040
So as long as you're paying
attention to the content.

00:21:49.040 --> 00:21:50.790
And that's actually
