00:26:45.290 --> 00:26:46.450
I loved it.

00:26:46.450 --> 00:26:50.240
It's talking about not just
IQ, all different kinds

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:52.617
of intelligences.

00:26:52.617 --> 00:26:54.200
These are all some
of the things we've

00:26:54.200 --> 00:26:58.280
identified as great positives--
access to information.

00:26:58.280 --> 00:26:59.280
You guys are at Google.

00:26:59.280 --> 00:27:00.130
You know that.

00:27:00.130 --> 00:27:01.260
Connect and collaborate.

00:27:01.260 --> 00:27:04.330
