00:27:13.490 --> 00:27:15.240
they're not getting
access to learning

00:27:15.240 --> 00:27:18.060
all about these things.

00:27:18.060 --> 00:27:22.900
So I'm gonna talk about video
games for this audience.

00:27:22.900 --> 00:27:24.850
Video games, this
is a slight aside,

00:27:24.850 --> 00:27:28.607
but I wanted to share this
