media, video games

00:28:57.390 --> 00:28:59.220
are always at the bottom.

00:28:59.220 --> 00:29:02.394
I mean, at the top
of the worst media.

00:29:02.394 --> 00:29:03.810
The other thing I
wanna talk about

00:29:03.810 --> 00:29:05.640
