00:29:21.130 --> 00:29:22.370
He likes video games.

00:29:22.370 --> 00:29:23.110
She doesn't.

00:29:23.110 --> 00:29:24.710
She plays on her phone.

00:29:24.710 --> 00:29:26.520
Or is it socialization?

00:29:26.520 --> 00:29:27.620
I don't think we know.

00:29:27.620 --> 00:29:30.290
We really, actually, don't know.

00:29:30.290 --> 00:29:34.450
But I googled for this talk,
