00:29:43.670 --> 00:29:46.290
The girls that do do
it, they feel isolated

00:29:46.290 --> 00:29:49.570
or they're objectified.

00:29:49.570 --> 00:29:53.790
So I think we may wanna
think about the culture

00:29:53.790 --> 00:29:55.410
and how to change it.

00:29:55.410 --> 00:29:57.280
So this is a comic,
