00:30:16.740 --> 00:30:20.210
So the bottom line is, remember
the positive, co-view, co-play.

00:30:20.210 --> 00:30:22.360
Watch movies and
TV with your kids.

00:30:22.360 --> 00:30:23.870
Narrate your values.

00:30:23.870 --> 00:30:25.970
Play games with your child.

00:30:25.970 --> 00:30:29.580
Don't assume your daughter
is not interested in gaming.

00:30:29.580 --> 00:30:33.230
And have fun together with them.

